Type: Package
Package: LLMRcontent
Title: LLM-Assisted Content Analysis for the Social Sciences
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ali", "Sanaei", , "sanaei@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Treats language-model labels as measurements for quantitative
    content analysis. Coding protocols are validated against held-out human
    labels, used for error-corrected prevalence estimates, and archived with
    the underlying call records.
